                                                                Requirments and precaution for an error-free experience 
Download the opencv framework in the terminal using :   pip install opencv-python
The haarcascade must be downlaoded in the same exceuting folders for prevents any errors
If Someone trying with the system images, change the directory in the code (line no 07) cv2.imread('Filename')
Also, Insert the images in the same folder
Size, images, haarcascade , color and frames are default to be desinged. You Can change upto your needs and wants
                                                                      Happy Coding And Enjoy Developing 
